title: 97:  Draft Sleepers & Bracket Champion Revealed
itunes:title: 97:  Draft Sleepers & Bracket Champion Revealed
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down their NFC & AFC South perfect pairings.  Plus, the guys discuss their top sleepers in the 2016 draft class.  DJ & Bucky also give out their Red Star defensive tackle prospects and reveal the winner of the Move The Stick prospect bracket.
